  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/c6d73d1f7768e70adbc632887e21d6ad.avif?t=1721936907\" width=616 height=366 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/b100127b5f24351ec7a37cac2d711a09.avif?t=1721936907\" width=614 height=106 /></span><br>Hi !<br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game set up in a futuristic world. Inspired by the great \"Dorfromantik\" we have decided to make this game to build our team with a limit of 6 months of development.<br><br>Build your archipelago while listening to relaxing synthwave music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/6e8a3dae0c4308e539f44d2cdf4f9302.avif?t=1721936907\" width=614 height=106 /></span><br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game where you place hexagonal tiles and win points by connecting the same elements.<br><br>You start with a limited number of tiles and the game ends when you reach 0. Some features will allow you to win more tiles so you can extend the game duration.<br>Make the best score before the end!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PERFECTS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/5118eaa8fe0d230a0dd0b1e41a9b1aaa.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/5118eaa8fe0d230a0dd0b1e41a9b1aaa.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/5118eaa8fe0d230a0dd0b1e41a9b1aaa.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make perfect tiles to win powers & a bonus of points and 1 more tile.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POWERS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/400d4d9e90b1abeccae0922bbdac59ae.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/400d4d9e90b1abeccae0922bbdac59ae.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/400d4d9e90b1abeccae0922bbdac59ae.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use powers that will be given to you with each perfect :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Refresh: change the current tile<br></li><li> Generate: select an empty spot and get a tile that fits perfectly<br></li><li> Delete: delete the selected tile.<br></li><li> Copy : copy an existing tile</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>QUESTS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/350535ca7efed86a7a941ef5db2985f3.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/350535ca7efed86a7a941ef5db2985f3.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/350535ca7efed86a7a941ef5db2985f3.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Win bonuses of points & tiles with quests.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Connect 2 Roads : place your ending point and place tiles to connect both points. The shortest path gives a bonus.<br></li><li> Connect 2 Canals : Place your ending point and place tiles to connect both points. All tiles give a bonus.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CREATIVE MODE </strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/a99bbd44a995becf53edc8155a68d198.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/a99bbd44a995becf53edc8155a68d198.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/a99bbd44a995becf53edc8155a68d198.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create your own islands with no limits in the creative mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/651af465172e009f518de1bda483144b.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/651af465172e009f518de1bda483144b.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/651af465172e009f518de1bda483144b.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/b7a2e0d0373266db66e6119eb2285e53.avif?t=1721936907\" width=614 height=106 /></span><br>There is a little more than an hour of original soundtrack in Hexocity, composed by Way16a's composer: Raphael Ledent.<br>Let yourself flow with the relaxing synthwave of Hexocity.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/c6d73d1f7768e70adbc632887e21d6ad.avif?t=1721936907\" width=616 height=366 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/b100127b5f24351ec7a37cac2d711a09.avif?t=1721936907\" width=614 height=106 /></span><br>Hi !<br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game set up in a futuristic world. Inspired by the great \"Dorfromantik\" we have decided to make this game to build our team with a limit of 6 months of development.<br><br>Build your archipelago while listening to relaxing synthwave music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.poster.avif?t=1721936907\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.webm?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/86cad26e4ae7804b80dbf52512c9dc0e.mp4?t=1721936907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/6e8a3dae0c4308e539f44d2cdf4f9302.avif?t=1721936907\" width=614 height=106 /></span><br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game where you place hexagonal tiles and win points by connecting the same elements.<br><br>You start with a limited number of tiles and the game ends when you reach 0. Some features will allow you to win more tiles so you can extend the game duration.<br>Make the best score before the end!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PERFECTS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb